{
  "id": 2679,
  "name": "Kystia Manaheart",
  "description": "Although an accomplished Magister, Kystia Manaheart was far too devoted to fel magic to give it up entirely. Little wonder she's become a staunch supporter and ally to underground fel smuggling operations in the Row.",
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "Overview",
      "body_text": "Kystia Manaheart is accompanied by her pet mana wyrm Nibbles, who is controlled by [Illicit Infusion]. When this infusion is removed, Nibbles breaks free of Kystia's control and reverts back to her light form to assist players in battle with [Light Infusion].",
      "spell": null,
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "Damage Dealers",
          "body_text": "$bullet; Kystia turns Nibbles hostile to players with [Illicit Infusion].\r\n$bullet; Avoid Nibbles' [Fel Spray].\r\n$bullet; Interrupt Kystia's [Mirror Images].",
          "spell": null,
          "sections": null
        },
        {
          "title": "Healers",
          "body_text": "$bullet; Kystia turns Nibbles hostile to players with [Illicit Infusion].\r\n$bullet; Avoid Nibbles' [Fel Spray].\r\n$bullet; Kystia inflicts heavy damage to all players while [Destabilized].",
          "spell": null,
          "sections": null
        },
        {
          "title": "Tank",
          "body_text": "$bullet; Kystia turns Nibbles hostile to players with [Illicit Infusion].\r\n$bullet; Avoid Nibbles' [Fel Spray].\r\n$bullet; Interrupt Kystia's [Mirror Images].",
          "spell": null,
          "sections": null
        }
      ]
    },
